{{Quote|One time, we were making a run of ''Barcarian claw salt''. You ever see any ''up close''? It ''looks'' like ''eyeballs''&mdash;which is bad enough&mdash;but the ''smell''... It'll just ''kill'' you. ''Real'' bad on ''Wookiees''. They have a better sense of smell than Humans.|[[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]], to [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]]|<ref name="AVS">''[[A Valentine Story]]''</ref>}}
'''Barcarian claw salt''' was a commodity from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Barcaria]]. It was said to resemble [[Eye/Legends|eyeballs]], and had a particularly pungent aroma, one that was even stronger to the sensitive smell of [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]].<ref name="AVS" />

[[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] were once running Barcarian claw salt when they were raided by the [[Natalon Core Bandits]].<ref name="AVS" />

